title: Achcham Yenbadhu Madamaiyada
subTitle: Rajinikanth and Leela, a young couple, embark on a road trip. However, little do they know that unfortunate instances are going to put their lives at stake.

title: Magarantham
subTitle: Shankar loves Kalpana but promises a dying father that he will marry the father's terminally ill daughter Geeta. While he marries both women, his care towards Geeta causes jealousy in Kalpana.

title: Malleswaran
subTitle: A woman, whose father dies mysteriously, falls in love with a man, Malli. Later, he adopts an abandoned baby while his friend, who killed the infant's parents, tries to separate them.

title: Teleshopping
subTitle: Learn about a wide selection of products and take advantage of a convenient method of shopping. A show for those who love to shop from the comforts of their home.

title: Ethiri
subTitle: Subramani poses as a goon to evict bachelor tenants from a Brahmin's house but instead helps one of them kidnap his lover from her marriage. However, chaos ensues when he kidnaps the wrong girl.

title: Mounam Pesiyadhe
subTitle: Gauthan, uninterested in romance, slowly finds his world shifting when Sandhya enters his life, but before he understands his feelings, family decisions complicate matters.

title: Arul
subTitle: Arul, the youngest of four brothers, faces the wrath of his father as he takes the blame for a mistake committed by one of his siblings. However, their relationship worsens when Arul is forced into politics.

title: Em Mahan
subTitle: Krishna is always worried and sad as his strict father does not miss a chance to scold him. His father goes overboard by chasing him out of the house when he learns about Krishna's love life.

title: Naan Mirugamaai Maara
subTitle: Bhoominathan seeks revenge after his brother gets murdered. So, he hires some contract killers but soon realises that his family's safety is on the line.

title: Thulluvadho Ilamai
subTitle: Six friends from high school decide to leave home and live together. But they soon understand the harsh realities of life and are forced to go back to their parents, who do not care for them.

title: Thulluvadho Ilamai

title: Manase Mounama
subTitle: Arun, a medical student, becomes the new college chairman despite receiving threats from Dhana, a gangster. When he sets out to kill Arun and meets with an accident, Arun ends up saving his life.

title: Manjal Veiyil
subTitle: Best friends Gayatri and Rajesh go to Ooty for her sister Savitri's wedding. However, the groom gets attracted to Gayatri and vows to marry her instead of her sister Savitri.

title: Teleshopping
subTitle: Learn about a wide selection of products and take advantage of a convenient method of shopping. A show for those who love to shop from the comforts of their home.

title: Manasellam
subTitle: Bala manages to find a place to stay after losing his bag with all his belongings. However, his roommates concoct a vicious plan and get him beaten to ruin his chances with their cute neighbour.

title: Vana Yuddham
subTitle: Veerappan, a poacher, chooses the path of crime and becomes a dangerous criminal. He systematically kills all the policemen who try to stop his evil ways and nab him.

title: Jallikattu
subTitle: A strong young man takes it upon himself to defeat a fierce bull and steal the bag of coins attached to its horns. His enemy wants him dead owing to his skills.

title: Poomagal Oorvalam
subTitle: Sarvanan, adopted by a childless couple, falls in love with Kavitha, the daughter of a caste-obsessed Sengodan. Soon, Sarvanan tries to change Sengodan's attitude in order to marry Kavitha.

title: Sabari
subTitle: Sabarivasan, a cardiologist, works in a government hospital during the day and runs a clinic at night. He attracts the enmity of a local goon when he gets the goon's partner arrested.

title: Poovellam Kettuppar
subTitle: Janaki and Krishna fall in love, unaware of the estranged relationship between their fathers. Later, they strive to convince their families to approve their relationship.

title: Poovellam Kettuppar

title: Markandeyan
subTitle: A man is adopted and raised by a gangster. However, complications arise when a rivalry ensues between him and the gangster's son.

title: Marumagale Vazhga
subTitle: Gopi and his brother Satyam get married but Gopi's wife is not treated well in the family. Lakshmi, Satyam's wife, realizes the same and tries to teach her mother-in-law a lesson.

title: Ranuva Veeran
subTitle: Raghu returns to his village and learns that people are being terrorised by a notorious gang. His world comes crashing down when he realises that his sister is in love with the leader of the gang.

title: Tiger Vishwa
subTitle: After studying in the US, Vishwa starts living with his brother's family and gets into a tiff with two gangs. While the gangsters set out to get him, Vishwa's lover's marriage is fixed by her father.

title: Oor Mariyadhai
subTitle: Rathnavelu loves Rasathi, who is in love with Kannan, brother of Veerapandi, an archrival of Rathnavelu. She is forcefully married to Rathnavelu, which leads to the death of Kannan.

title: Sivasakthi
subTitle: Sakthi, a police officer, befriends Siva, a smuggler, in order to gain his trust and get evidence against him. But soon, their friendship turns into a genuine one.

title: Priyamaana Thozhi
subTitle: Ashok and Julie are childhood friends and she is set to marry Michael. However, when Ashok gets selected to the Indian cricket team instead of Michael, Ashok gives up his career to save her marriage.

title: Neerparavai
subTitle: A fisherman's widow visits the beach every day, hoping that her husband might return, despite being aware of his death and the weird looks from her community.
